--- !u!114 &1650242155321414091
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1650242155410224631}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 044c62b2badefb240b6d935ccbb3d9ca, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  textSource: {fileID: 1650242155321414082}
  storyText: {fileID: 1650242155399086812}
  storyArray:
  - In the quaint town of Ravenville, resides a young and vibrant girl named Nia.
  - From childhood dreams to a daily hustle, I passionately sketch designs and craft
    outfits for thrift stores, determined to make it big in the dynamic world of
    fashion.
  - But, Ravenville is far from the fashion capital I aspire to be a part of.
  - Supported by my best friends Sarah and Alex, we share laughs, dreams, and secrets
    as a close trio, but we understand a bit of magic is needed to turn our dreams
    into reality.
  - Lately, I've felt a lack of accomplishment in my life, contrasting with childhood
    dreams of exploring new places, connecting with diverse people, and carving a
    name for myself in the fashion industry.
  - One day to cheer me up, Sarah suggested visiting a local antique store to browse
    through the items they have.
  - "There everything looks good but one of which, a bracelet, catches my eye and
    I\u2019m drawn towards it."
  - The shopkeeper reveals that the bracelet possesses magical powers, able to teleport
    someone to their heart's desired location, contingent on unwavering self-belief
    and a genuine desire to achieve something.
  - Upon trying it on, all of a sudden we got teleported to a whole new place we
    never saw before.
  - '*The shopkeeper stood there in awe as the trio got teleported right before his
    eyes.*'
  speedPerCharactor: 0.05
  tapAnim: {fileID: 4015928803092899524}
  noteAnim: {fileID: 1650242155410224635}
